1. * Kasnim* na posao. (I'm late for work.)
2. Pre nego što *kasnim* na događaj, moram da pripremim stvari. (Before I'm late for the event, I need to prepare things.)
3. Ona je *kasnila* na rođendan svoje ćerke. (She was late to her daughter's birthday.)
4. Oni su *kasnili* na sastanak za više od sat vremena. (They were late to the meeting for more than an hour.)
5. *Kasni* da odeš u školu? (Are you late to go to school?)
6. Oni su *kasnili* za deset minuta. (They were late for ten minutes.)